  "special": {
    "title": "Surpresssing Fires!!!",
    "description": "Always incendiary. Fires a main bullet that quickly splits into three sideways-fanning projectiles, which then explode after a short delay. The main bullet itself has no splash."
  },
  "notes": "It uses the same skin as a purple Bandit rifle. The split and detonation are based on flight time rather than distance, so higher projectile speed pushes the explosions farther out. It synergizes well with Make it Sparkle because Deathtrap only needs to be near the line of fire. The first bullet has no splash, but the three spawned bullets each deal full gun damage and add their own splash detonation. Grenade damage bonuses do not increase that splash. Both the bullets and the explosions can ignite.",
